last_episode_to_air.overview: It's finally Humphrey and Martha's wedding day – what could possibly go wrong? Other than a museum heist, cyber crime and an unexpected arrival.

name: Beyond Paradise
overview: After leaving paradise and seeking a quieter life, Humphrey has taken a job as Detective Inspector in his fiancée Martha's hometown. But with the high crime rate, maybe things will be louder than expected.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Humphrey Goodman joins the police in fiancée Martha's hometown of Shipton Abbott in Devon.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: DI Humphrey Goodman and his fiancée Martha settle into their new life by the Devon coast.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: A new adventure awaits as DI Humphrey Goodman and Martha leave London for Devon. Humphrey dives into his first case, which involves an unusual prime suspect: a 17th-century witch.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Humphrey and his team are baffled by the mysterious disappearance of an entire family. Martha prepares for the launch of her café but is thrown when a face from the past shows up.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: The community of Shipton Abbott is rocked when a beloved painting disappears in a seemingly impossible heist. Humphrey tries his best to find some common ground with Archie.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Humphrey investigates the death of an unidentified man found in the centre of a crop circle. Meanwhile, Archie helps Martha prepare for a visit from a food critic.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Panic spreads when an arsonist targets three businesses, bizarrely invoking the Three Little Pigs fable. Meanwhile, Martha has some serious thinking to do.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: A house is burgled but the prime suspect was locked up in a police cell at the time. It’s up to Esther to rally a devastated Humphrey and solve this impossible crime.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: Humphrey Goodman joins the police in fiancée Martha's hometown of Shipton Abbott in Devon.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: The Shipton Abbott Players rope in Humphrey to play a detective, but the fictional crime becomes real when the amateur murder victim gets a real knife in his back.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: When an amateur psychic’s unsettling predictions for a grieving woman’s future start to come true, Humphrey must uncover the truth before it’s too late.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: When a dying woman goes missing from a local fishing trawler, Humphrey suspects there’s more to her disappearance than meets the eye.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: When a priest at a Catholic boarding school goes missing, Humphrey’s team explores a connection between his disappearance and an ancient local legend.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: On a moor outside of Shipton Abbott, a woman is found with an arrow in her back and no sign of who might have shot her.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: It's finally Humphrey and Martha's wedding day – what could possibly go wrong? Other than a museum heist, cyber crime and an unexpected arrival.
